    tc:statement """Canonical flows for common billing issues without exposing PII or promising credits.

Playbook: Get invoice PDF
  1) Ask for masked account identifier (e.g., ticket or org slug).
  2) Guide to: Settings → Billing → Invoices → "Download PDF".
  3) If missing, create ticket for Billing with masked reference.

Playbook: Refund request (within policy)
  1) Acknowledge and summarize the reason.
  2) Link refunds policy (exact section) and timeframe.
  3) Create Billing ticket; do not promise outcome; share reference ID.

