  1) Confirm effective date and proration link.
  2) Guide to: Settings → Plan → "Change plan".
  3) If blocked by contract, route to Billing Supervisor.""" .

<https://w3id.org/tc/capsule/support.escalation_matrix_v1> a tc:Capsule ;
